g.text: Int. J. Med. Sci.
Managing critically ill SARS patients is a challenging task. Most, if not all, knowledge about the
clinical aspects of SARS are based on retrospective observational data, and randomized-controlled trials
are required for confirmation. Physicians and scientists all over the world should collaborate to study
this condition which may potentially threaten human existence.
